{"tid":1495502,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港係世界上最安全的城市。每個香港人奉公守法，但換黎的，只係殘暴不仁的制度暴力剝削","createTime":"2019-08-22T05:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T06:06:16.000Z","uid":149978,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd1a5ae3f262f8456bd4a9041128c1e3ccaeb8fe","tid":1495502,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:50:05.000Z","msg":"香港係連續十幾年，被多間機構世界上最安全的城市。<br />\n吸引了世界的眼球。<br />\n很多人羡慕，想黎定居。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人努力付出，奉公守法，換黎係咩 ？<br />\n<br />\n係業主每年加你租20%<br />\n係樓價每年升20%<br />\n係物價每年升10%以上<br />\n係住屋環境每年細20%<br />\n係大宅變細宅，細宅變棺材房<br />\n係大量遊客迫到你連去廁所都要排長龍<br />\n係大量遊客迫到你要買貴奶粉，又貴又差的貨<br />\n<br />\n呢個政府設計的社會制度，<br />\n係一個以惡報善的制度，<br />\n付出不單無回報，還被進一步剝削欺壓，<br />\n點解香港人仲要繼續付出？<br />\n點解香港人仲唔出聲反對 ？"},{"pid":"af7f09f0c8f602a700306f6128d5059cd5fd7587","tid":1495502,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU，而家搭車犯法呀?</strong></span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrRtRqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrRtRqw.jpg&h=a938cd9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTCkHxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTCkHxb.jpg&h=73ff0599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00prC5w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00prC5w.jpg&h=ccabd632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJckHxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJckHxb.jpg&h=e84b0cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x3bJFtJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx3bJFtJ.jpg&h=400310ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mzORrS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mzORrS.jpg&h=e1aa2d33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvSwHez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvSwHez.png&h=660b03dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41ceee0c7bfbbfd3dab672c982d84c31f8017323","tid":1495502,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:54:50.000Z","msg":"澳門都識每年派10000蚊<br />\n新加坡都識俾每人有組屋住<br />\n<br />\n香港派那4000蚊都又呢又路又煩<br />\n<br />\n香港繁榮，只會讓業主繼續加你租<br />\n有樓的，只要你唔係大屋的，<br />\n香港繁榮，換大些的屋的希望就離你更遠。"},{"pid":"3f5fc69a57e483d115f481488c62b2a739caeb27","tid":1495502,"uid":253561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:56:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cd75306dd529009d30013e418a627057c677b26","tid":1495502,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:03:29.000Z","msg":"目前政府設計的制度<br />\n香港越繁榮，香港大部分的人就越痛苦<br />\n香港越繁榮，生活更困難。<br />\n<br />\n不論這制度是港英設計，定特區加劇，都一樣係暴政。<br />\n香港人，請向暴政說不，向制度暴力說不"},{"pid":"7fad53412cc7917b7ff3a90fd8fd4c70fdd2ca70","tid":1495502,"uid":176681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:06:16.000Z","msg":"吸引了世界的<del>眼球</del>目光<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}